Text:
Yes, they're RARs, but all you have to do is unpack them. Nothing complicated about that.
No conversion required as long as you can play .MKV files, which I think almost everyone can. .MKV has been the standard for high-def video for, what? Like 3 years now. Quit your whinging.

@nflfan - wow, way to complain about something that's free, and after somebody took the time and effort to capture this, encode it, and upload it here, in high definition format no less. If you don't want it, then don't download it. But many of us are grateful to have a source for games like this -- judging by how there are over 110 folks uploading and downloading this at the moment.

@leonidas_led_300

In future I suggest you read and understand other's comments before jumping in. Personally rars are no great hassle for me but may be for some, hence my  comments, and far from whinging, I was the first to thank dani00cl for this game.

In short, engage brain before passing comment.
